(# Zero to Hero Study Handbook: lora-dpo-json-extraction) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Module 1: Foundations & Architecture) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 1\) What this project does) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This repository builds an end-to-end fine-tuning pipeline for **structured JSON extraction** from ) Tj
T*
(support tickets using:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Baseline generation \(no adapter\)) Tj
T*
(- Supervised fine-tuning \(SFT\) with LoRA/QLoRA adapters) Tj
T*
(- Preference optimization with DPO) Tj
T*
(- Stage-by-stage evaluation with persisted prediction artifacts and summary metrics) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Core runtime entrypoint is ) Tj
T*
([`src/lora_dpo_json_extraction/run_pipeline.py`]\(src/lora_dpo_json_extraction/run_pipeline.py\), ) Tj
T*
(usually called with:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(uv run python -m lora_dpo_json_extraction.run_pipeline --config configs/default.yaml) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 2\) Main use cases) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Learn a full adapter-tuning workflow \(data -> SFT -> DPO -> evaluation\).) Tj
T*
(- Compare baseline vs SFT vs DPO on JSON extraction metrics.) Tj
T*
(- Study deterministic synthetic data generation and optional internet dataset ingestion ) Tj
T*
(\(`PolyAI/banking77`\).) Tj
T*
(- Reuse the pipeline skeleton for other extraction schemas/tasks.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 3\) Core paradigms and patterns used in this repo) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- **Pipeline orchestration pattern**: `run\(\)` in `run_pipeline.py` coordinates fixed stages and ) Tj
T*
(writes all artifacts in one run directory.) Tj
T*
(- **Config-first design**: `ProjectConfig` \(Pydantic\) in `settings.py` validates YAML config into ) Tj
T*
(typed objects.) Tj
T*
(- **Hybrid style \(functional + lightweight OOP\)**:) Tj
T*
(  - Functional helpers in `data.py`, `evaluate.py`, `utils.py`.) Tj
T*
(  - OOP-like dataset/collator classes in `datasets.py`.) Tj
T*
(- **Adapter-based fine-tuning**: `models.py` builds PEFT LoRA adapters on top of a base causal LM.) Tj
T*
(- **Deterministic data pipeline**: `set_seed\(\)` plus deterministic `random.Random\(seed\)` ) Tj
T*
(generation/sampling.) Tj
T*
(- **Evaluation with explicit audit artifacts**: `evaluate_stage\(\)` computes rates and writes ) Tj
T*
(`predictions_{stage}.jsonl`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 4\) Architecture: components and interactions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Key modules:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `settings.py`: typed config models and YAML loading.) Tj
T*
(- `run_pipeline.py`: orchestration, run directory creation, final reporting.) Tj
T*
(- `data.py`: synthetic/Banking77 split generation + DPO preference pair construction.) Tj
T*
(- `datasets.py`: PyTorch dataset/collator wrappers for SFT and DPO.) Tj
T*
(- `models.py`: tokenizer/base model loading, LoRA/QLoRA setup, adapter loading for inference.) Tj
T*
(- `train.py`: SFT and DPO training loops.) Tj
T*
(- `evaluate.py`: generation-based evaluation and metric computation.) Tj
T*
(- `utils.py`: seed, file I/O, JSON extraction helper.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Main flow diagram:) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
