(## Module 3: Core Execution Flows) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Flow A: Entry point and orchestration \(`run_pipeline.py`\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. `main\(\)` calls `parse_args\(\)`, which defines `--config` defaulting to `configs/default.yaml`.) Tj
T*
(2. `main\(\)` loads config via `load_config\(args.config\)` from `settings.py`.) Tj
T*
(3. `run\(cfg\)` executes the full pipeline:) Tj
T*
(   - `set_seed\(cfg.seed\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `_make_run_dir\(cfg\)` creates `outputs/run_<YYYYmmdd_HHMMSS>/`) Tj
T*
(   - `build_splits\(...\)` creates `train`, `val`, `test`) Tj
T*
(   - `build_preference_split\(splits["train"], seed=cfg.seed\)` creates DPO pairs) Tj
T*
(   - `_save_data_artifacts\(...\)` writes data JSONL files) Tj
T*
(   - `evaluate_stage\(stage="base", ...\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `train_sft\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `evaluate_stage\(stage="sft", adapter_dir=...\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `train_dpo\(..., sft_adapter_dir=...\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `evaluate_stage\(stage="dpo", adapter_dir=...\)`) Tj
T*
(   - writes `metrics_summary.json` and `RUN_REPORT.md`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Short code fragment \(real logic shape\):) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```python) Tj
T*
(base_metrics = evaluate_stage\(cfg=cfg, stage="base", rows=splits["test"], output_dir=run_dir\)) Tj
T*
(sft_summary = train_sft\(cfg, splits["train"], splits["val"], run_dir\)) Tj
T*
(sft_metrics = evaluate_stage\(cfg=cfg, stage="sft", rows=splits["test"], output_dir=run_dir, ) Tj
T*
(adapter_dir=sft_summary["adapter_dir"]\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Flow B: Data construction \(`data.py`\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#### B1\) SFT/Eval split generation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`build_splits\(...\)` dispatches by `source`:) Tj
T*
() Tj
