(- `"synthetic"`: calls `generate_examples\(total_size, seed\)` and slices into train/val/test.) Tj
T*
(- `"banking77"` or aliases: calls `build_banking77_splits\(...\)` which uses ) Tj
T*
(`datasets.load_dataset\(...\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Synthetic row shape:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```python) Tj
T*
({) Tj
T*
(  "prompt": str,) Tj
T*
(  "response": str,   # JSON string) Tj
T*
(  "target": {) Tj
T*
(    "intent": str,) Tj
T*
(    "priority": str,      # "low" | "medium" | "high") Tj
T*
(    "product": str,) Tj
T*
(    "needs_human": bool) Tj
T*
(  }) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`build_prompt\(ticket\)` injects ticket text into `PROMPT_TEMPLATE` and ends with `JSON:` so the model) Tj
T*
( is guided to produce JSON only.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#### B2\) Banking77 mapping) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(In `_banking77_row_to_payload\(text, label_name\)`:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Normalize label with `_normalize_intent`.) Tj
T*
(2. Map to grouped `intent` via `_derive_intent_group_from_banking77_label`.) Tj
T*
(3. Derive `priority` via `_derive_priority_from_banking77`.) Tj
T*
(4. Derive `product` via `_derive_product_from_banking77_intent`.) Tj
T*
(5. Derive `needs_human` via `_derive_needs_human_from_banking77`.) Tj
T*
(6. Validate via `TicketExtraction.model_validate\(...\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#### B3\) DPO preference pair generation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`build_preference_split\(train_rows, seed\)` creates rows with:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```python) Tj
T*
({) Tj
T*
(  "prompt": str,) Tj
T*
(  "chosen": str,      # row["response"] \(correct JSON string\)) Tj
T*
(  "rejected": str,    # intentionally weaker variant) Tj
T*
(  "target": {...}     # same target dict) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`_build_rejected\(...\)` uses one of:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `wrong_field`) Tj
T*
(- `missing_field`) Tj
T*
(- `extra_text` \(prepends non-JSON text before JSON\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Flow C: SFT training \(`train.py` + `datasets.py` + `models.py`\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. `train_sft\(...\)` loads tokenizer and LoRA model:) Tj
T*
(   - `tokenizer = load_tokenizer\(cfg.model.name\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `model = build_lora_model\(cfg.model, for_training=True\)`) Tj
T*
(2. Creates `SFTDataset` for train/val and `DataLoader` with `SFTCollator`.) Tj
T*
(3. `SFTDataset.__getitem__` encodes `prompt` + `response + eos`, and applies **response-only loss**:) Tj
T*
(   - prompt labels are `-100` \(ignored by CE loss\)) Tj
ET
