(   - response token labels are actual token ids) Tj
T*
(4. Training loop does:) Tj
T*
(   - forward pass) Tj
T*
(   - loss scaling by `gradient_accumulation_steps`) Tj
T*
(   - `loss.backward\(\)`) Tj
T*
(   - grad clipping, optimizer/scheduler steps) Tj
T*
(5. Validation loss via `_evaluate_sft_loss`.) Tj
T*
(6. Saves adapter to `run_dir / "sft_adapter"` and tokenizer to `run_dir / "tokenizer"`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(SFT summary output shape:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```python) Tj
T*
({) Tj
T*
(  "adapter_dir": str,) Tj
T*
(  "tokenizer_dir": str,) Tj
T*
(  "history": [{"epoch": float, "train_loss": float, "val_loss": float}, ...],) Tj
T*
(  "global_steps": int) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Flow D: DPO training \(`train.py`\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. `train_dpo\(...\)` loads:) Tj
T*
(   - policy model from base + SFT adapter \(`is_trainable=True`\)) Tj
T*
(   - reference model from base + SFT adapter \(`is_trainable=False`, frozen params\)) Tj
T*
(2. Builds `DPODataset` + `DPOCollator`.) Tj
T*
(3. Per batch:) Tj
T*
(   - compute chosen/rejected sequence log-probs for policy and reference via ) Tj
T*
(`_sequence_log_probs\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(   - compute advantage:) Tj
T*
(     - `\(chosen_pi - rejected_pi\) - \(chosen_ref - rejected_ref\)`) Tj
T*
(   - DPO loss:) Tj
T*
(     - `-logsigmoid\(cfg.train.dpo_beta * advantage\).mean\(\)`) Tj
T*
(4. Runs optimizer/scheduler steps and records epoch loss.) Tj
T*
(5. Saves adapter to `run_dir / "dpo_adapter"`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(DPO summary output shape:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```python) Tj
T*
({) Tj
T*
(  "adapter_dir": str,) Tj
T*
(  "history": [{"epoch": float, "dpo_loss": float}, ...],) Tj
T*
(  "global_steps": int) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Flow E: Evaluation and metrics \(`evaluate.py`\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`evaluate_stage\(cfg, stage, rows, output_dir, adapter_dir=None\)`:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Loads tokenizer \(`load_tokenizer`\).) Tj
T*
(2. Builds model:) Tj
T*
(   - `stage="base"` -> `load_base_model\(..., for_training=False\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `stage in {"sft","dpo"}` -> `load_adapter_for_inference\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(3. For each row:) Tj
T*
(   - generate output with `_generate_prediction\(...\)` \(`do_sample=False`, `temperature=0.0`\)) Tj
T*
(   - parse first balanced JSON object using `extract_first_json_object\(...\)` then `json.loads\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(   - normalize with `_coerce_prediction\(...\)`) Tj
T*
(4. Computes metrics and writes `predictions_{stage}.jsonl`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
