T*
(- `CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES`) Tj
T*
(  - Used in README command example to force CPU path \(`CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=''`\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 4\) Configuration files and key controls) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `configs/default.yaml`) Tj
T*
(  - Uses local Qwen snapshot path in `model.name`) Tj
T*
(  - `model.use_qlora: true`) Tj
T*
(  - No explicit `data.source`, so `DataConfig` default applies: `"synthetic"`) Tj
T*
(- `configs/internet_banking77.yaml`) Tj
T*
(  - `data.source: banking77`) Tj
T*
(  - `data.hf_dataset: PolyAI/banking77`) Tj
T*
(  - Uses `distilgpt2` and LoRA-only \(`use_qlora: false`\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 5\) Typical run commands) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Synthetic/default path:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(HF_HUB_DISABLE_XET=1 uv run python -m lora_dpo_json_extraction.run_pipeline --config ) Tj
T*
(configs/default.yaml) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Banking77 path:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES='' HF_HUB_DISABLE_XET=1 uv run python -m lora_dpo_json_extraction.run_pipeline ) Tj
T*
(--config configs/internet_banking77.yaml) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 6\) Runtime artifacts written by pipeline) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Under `outputs/run_<timestamp>/`:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `config_snapshot.json`) Tj
T*
(- `run.log`) Tj
T*
(- `metrics_summary.json`) Tj
T*
(- `RUN_REPORT.md`) Tj
T*
(- `predictions_base.jsonl`) Tj
T*
(- `predictions_sft.jsonl`) Tj
T*
(- `predictions_dpo.jsonl`) Tj
T*
(- `sft_training_summary.json`) Tj
T*
(- `dpo_training_summary.json`) Tj
T*
(- `sft_adapter/`) Tj
T*
(- `dpo_adapter/`) Tj
T*
(- `tokenizer/`) Tj
T*
(- `data/train_sft.jsonl`) Tj
T*
(- `data/val_sft.jsonl`) Tj
T*
(- `data/test_eval.jsonl`) Tj
T*
(- `data/train_dpo_prefs.jsonl`) Tj
T*
