T*
() Tj
T*
(6. **Metric math check**) Tj
T*
(   - Question: How are `valid_json_rate`, `schema_match_rate`, and `field_accuracy` computed?) Tj
T*
(   - Files: `src/lora_dpo_json_extraction/evaluate.py`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. **Adapter loading path**) Tj
T*
(   - Question: How does evaluation decide between base model and adapter-based model loading?) Tj
T*
(   - Files: `src/lora_dpo_json_extraction/evaluate.py`, `src/lora_dpo_json_extraction/models.py`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. **Artifact contract**) Tj
T*
(   - Question: List all files/subfolders that `run_pipeline.py` guarantees to write when stages ) Tj
T*
(complete.) Tj
T*
