BT
/F1 10 Tf
50 800 Td
() Tj
T*
(### 3\) Model answer outlines) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. **Default data source answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - `DataConfig.source` default is `"synthetic"` in `settings.py`.) Tj
T*
(   - `configs/default.yaml` does not override it.) Tj
T*
(   - `build_splits\(\)` receives this value and follows synthetic path.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. **Stage order answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - `evaluate_stage\("base"\)` -> `train_sft\(\)` -> `evaluate_stage\("sft"\)` -> `train_dpo\(\)` -> ) Tj
T*
(`evaluate_stage\("dpo"\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. **Response-only loss answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - `labels = [-100] * prompt_len + input_ids[prompt_len:]`.) Tj
T*
(   - `-100` tells CE loss to ignore prompt tokens.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. **Rejected response modes answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - Wrong field value mutation.) Tj
T*
(   - Missing a required field.) Tj
T*
(   - Prefixing extra non-JSON text before JSON payload.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. **Banking77 mapping answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - Normalize label text.) Tj
T*
(   - Map to grouped intent using keyword rules.) Tj
T*
(   - Derive priority from intent group and urgency keywords.) Tj
T*
(   - Derive product from keyword mapping.) Tj
T*
(   - Derive needs_human from group/keywords/priority.) Tj
T*
(   - Validate final dict against `TicketExtraction`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6. **Metric math answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - `valid_json_rate = valid_json / len\(rows\)`) Tj
T*
(   - `schema_match_rate = schema_match / len\(rows\)` where schema match means exact expected key set.) Tj
T*
(   - `field_accuracy = field_hits / \(len\(rows\) * len\(EXPECTED_KEYS\)\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. **Adapter loading answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - In `_build_model`, stage `"base"` calls `load_base_model\(...\)`.) Tj
T*
(   - Other stages require `adapter_dir` and call `load_adapter_for_inference\(...\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. **Artifact contract answer outline**) Tj
T*
(   - Core outputs from orchestrator: config snapshot, logs, summary/report, predictions.) Tj
T*
(   - Training adds `sft_adapter/`, `dpo_adapter/`, tokenizer and training summary JSON files.) Tj
T*
(   - Data artifacts saved under `data/` JSONL files.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Understanding Checklist) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Use this checklist before claiming mastery:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Can you explain what `run\(\)` in `run_pipeline.py` does without looking at the file?) Tj
T*
