T*
(- Can you explain why `TicketExtraction` validation is used in data building?) Tj
T*
(- Can you describe exactly how SFT loss masking is implemented?) Tj
T*
(- Can you explain the difference between policy and reference models in `train_dpo\(\)`?) Tj
T*
(- Can you derive DPO loss terms from `_sequence_log_probs\(\)` outputs?) Tj
T*
(- Can you explain how prediction text is converted into `prediction_json` safely?) Tj
T*
(- Can you compute each evaluation metric manually for a tiny 2-row example?) Tj
T*
(- Can you list which output files are used for debugging bad model behavior?) Tj
T*
(- Can you state which environment variables are optional and where they are used?) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
